{"tid":289972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 克 儉 太 太 病 逝","createTime":"2017-06-19T12:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T18:30:50.000Z","uid":23707,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c16bd300e9b6e8772f5f0adcac9f2cf28ce6e409","tid":289972,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"吳克儉今年3月丁母憂之後，再經歷喪妻之痛。教育局證實，教育局局長吳克儉太太今日（6月27日）下午病逝，吳克儉暫時休假處理家庭事宜，但仍會與暫代局長一職的副局長楊潤雄保持緊密聯繫，處理教育局事務。 教育局局長吳克儉原定今日下午出席「夢想起飛GO！GO！GO！」的學生生涯規劃活動，但因太太病危，需請假處理，而有關活動改由教育局署理常任秘書長黃邱慧清出席。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/article/06-27-2016/31319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-27-2016%2F31319&d=vpd5XgWtkLViUnhvB70SY0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e6941d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">passiontimes.hk/article/06-27-2016/31319</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2016"},{"pid":"24b6bbb02d87edbcbe59c4c8e320d9a316350833","tid":289972,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb920098a6f0f1ab1f6970cbb8ce0deaa5522141","tid":289972,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"死哂全家未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6ba00305134af3305706d5e4db4c0b0130aacf","tid":289972,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d885354b5579452638c6a83e6e33205c7893d511","tid":289972,"uid":93890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"與自殺學生會面姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30dc89cffde03be6026ea05a74578c5706d82c3","tid":289972,"uid":110192,"like":0,"dislike":0